{"title":"php特性","uid":"cd1787040df7226f24b8f728e6089b8f","slug":"php特性","date":"2024-01-21T16:07:22.000Z","updated":"2024-01-21T16:22:16.087Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/php特性.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"php特性\"><a href=\"#php特性\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"php特性\"></a>php特性</h1><h2 id=\"1-preg-match\"><a href=\"#1-preg-match\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.preg_match\"></a>1.preg_match</h2><p><code>preg_match</code> 是 PHP 中用于执行正则表达式匹配的函数。它的主要特性包括：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>正则表达式匹配：<code>preg_match</code> 允许你使用正则表达式来匹配字符串。你可以定义自定义的正则表达式模式，以满足特定的匹配需求。</li>\n<li>匹配检测：<code>preg_match</code> 用于检查字符串是否匹配给定的正则表达式。如果匹配成功，函数返回 <code>1</code>，否则返回 <code>0</code>。</li>\n<li>第一个匹配：如果正则表达式匹配多次，<code>preg_match</code> 仅返回第一个匹配项。这在查找第一个匹配项时很有用。</li>\n<li>匹配数组：你还可以使用 <code>preg_match</code> 的函数变体来匹配所有出现的匹配项，而不仅仅是第一个匹配项。例如，<code>preg_match_all</code> 返回所有匹配项的数组。</li>\n<li>匹配参数：<code>preg_match</code> 接受正则表达式、输入字符串和可选的匹配结果数组作为参数。如果指定了匹配结果数组，匹配结果将存储在该数组中。</li>\n<li>匹配修饰符：正则表达式可以附加修饰符，以控制匹配的方式。例如，**<code>i</code> 修饰符用于不区分大小写匹配，<code>g</code> 修饰符用于全局匹配等**。这些修饰符可以在正则表达式模式中指定。</li>\n<li>异常处理：<code>preg_match</code> 可以用于处理异常情况，例如匹配失败或出现错误。你可以根据返回值来判断是否匹配成功，并采取相应的措施。</li>\n<li>完全匹配：默认情况下，<code>preg_match</code> 要求正则表达式完全匹配整个字符串。你可以使用 <code>^</code> 和 <code>$</code> 锚点来指定只匹配字符串的开头或结尾。</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"1-只检测数字\"><a href=\"#1-只检测数字\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.只检测数字\"></a>1.只检测数字</h3><figure class=\"highlight php\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">include</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;flag.php&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">highlight_file</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">__FILE__</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">isset</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$_GET</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;num&#x27;</span>]))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"variable\">$num</span> = <span class=\"variable\">$_GET</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;num&#x27;</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">preg_match</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;/[0-9]/&quot;</span>, <span class=\"variable\">$num</span>))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">die</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;no no no!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">intval</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$num</span>))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"variable\">$flag</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>用数组绕过<strong>num[]&#x3D;1</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"2-只检测字母\"><a href=\"#2-只检测字母\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.只检测字母\"></a>2.只检测字母</h3><figure class=\"highlight php\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">preg_match</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;/[a-z]/i&quot;</span>, <span class=\"variable\">$num</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"2-不能是字符串，但是转化成数字要等于\"><a href=\"#2-不能是字符串，但是转化成数字要等于\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.不能是字符串，但是转化成数字要等于\"></a>2.不能是字符串，但是转化成数字要等于</h2><figure class=\"highlight php\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">include</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;flag.php&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">highlight_file</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">__FILE__</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">isset</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$_GET</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;num&#x27;</span>]))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"variable\">$num</span> = <span class=\"variable\">$_GET</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;num&#x27;</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$num</span>===<span class=\"string\">&quot;4476&quot;</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">die</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;no no no!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">intval</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$num</span>,<span class=\"number\">0</span>)===<span class=\"number\">4476</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"variable\">$flag</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">intval</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$num</span>,<span class=\"number\">0</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>用数字后面带字母绕过<strong>num&#x3D;4476a</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"3-对于-i和-im绕过\"><a href=\"#3-对于-i和-im绕过\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.对于&#x2F;i和&#x2F;im绕过\"></a>3.对于&#x2F;i和&#x2F;im绕过</h2><p>在正则表达式中，”&#x2F;im” 和 “&#x2F;i” 是两种不同的修饰符，它们在匹配文本时有不同的作用：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code>/i</code> 修饰符：<ul>\n<li>“i” 代表 “不区分大小写”（case-insensitive），意味着不考虑字母的大小写，只匹配字母的字面值。例如，正则表达式 <code>/abc/i</code> 会匹配 “abc”、”AbC”、”ABC” 等所有大小写组合。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code>/m</code> 修饰符：<ul>\n<li>“m” 代表 “多行模式”（multiline mode），主要影响正则表达式中的锚点字符，如 “^” 和 “$”。在多行模式下，”^” 匹配每行的开头，”$” 匹配每行的结尾，而不仅仅是整个输入的开头和结尾。这对于处理包含多行文本的情况非常有用。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>如果你同时使用了 “&#x2F;im” 修饰符，它会同时启用 “不区分大小写” 和 “多行模式”。这意味着你的正则表达式将以不区分大小写的方式匹配文本，并且 “^” 和 “$” 将匹配每行的开头和结尾。</p>\n<p>示例：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight php\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$text</span> = <span class=\"string\">&quot;Hello\\nWorld\\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$pattern</span> = <span class=\"string\">&#x27;/world/im&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">preg_match</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$pattern</span>, <span class=\"variable\">$text</span>)) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;Match found!&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;No match found.&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>在上面的示例中，由于使用了 “&#x2F;im” 修饰符，正则表达式 <code>/world/im</code> 同时不区分大小写匹配和多行模式匹配，所以它能够匹配 “World”，即使 “W” 是大写的，并且它匹配每行的开头。</p>\n<p><strong>在这里注意”\\n”的URL编码是”%0A”</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight php\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">show_source</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">__FILE__</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">include</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;flag.php&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$a</span>=<span class=\"variable\">$_GET</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;cmd&#x27;</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">preg_match</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;/^php$/im&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"variable\">$a</span>))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">preg_match</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;/^php$/i&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"variable\">$a</span>))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;hacker&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"variable\">$flag</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;nonononono&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>我们可以根据他第一个可以多行匹配而第二个不行来绕过<strong>cmd&#x3D;1%0Aphp</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"4-intval-variable-base-绕过\"><a href=\"#4-intval-variable-base-绕过\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.intval(variable, base)绕过\"></a>4.intval(variable, base)绕过</h2><p><code>intval</code> 是 PHP 中的一个函数，用于将一个值转换为整数。它的作用是取一个变量，并尝试将其转换为整数类型。如果变量无法转换为整数，<code>intval</code> 返回 0。这函数通常用于确保一个值是整数类型，以便进行数学运算或其他需要整数的操作。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>variable</code>: 要转换为整数的变量或值。</li>\n<li><code>base</code> (可选): 指定变量的基数（进制）。默认情况下，<code>intval</code> 使用十进制。你可以提供不同的基数，如 2（二进制）、8（八进制）或 16（十六进制）等。</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight php\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">include</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;flag.php&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">highlight_file</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">__FILE__</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">isset</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$_GET</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;num&#x27;</span>]))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"variable\">$num</span> = <span class=\"variable\">$_GET</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;num&#x27;</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$num</span>==<span class=\"number\">4476</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">die</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;no no no!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">intval</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$num</span>,<span class=\"number\">0</span>)==<span class=\"number\">4476</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"variable\">$flag</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">intval</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$num</span>,<span class=\"number\">0</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><code>intval($num, 0)</code> 中的第二个参数（基数）是 0，这意味着 PHP 会尝试自动检测输入的字符串的进制（基数）并将其转换为整数。如果字符串以 “0x” 开头，PHP 将将其视为十六进制。<strong>如果以 “0” 开头但不是 “0x”，PHP 将将其视为八进制</strong>。否则，将其视为十进制。</p>\n<p>所以这道题我们不能直接输入4476，而是要输入他的十六进制数0x117c，从而绕过第一个判断并符合第二个判断<strong>num&#x3D;0x117c</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"八进制绕过\"><a href=\"#八进制绕过\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"八进制绕过\"></a>八进制绕过</h3><figure class=\"highlight php\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">include</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;flag.php&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">highlight_file</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">__FILE__</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">isset</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$_GET</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;num&#x27;</span>]))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"variable\">$num</span> = <span class=\"variable\">$_GET</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;num&#x27;</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$num</span>==<span class=\"number\">4476</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">die</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;no no no!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">preg_match</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;/[a-z]/i&quot;</span>, <span class=\"variable\">$num</span>))&#123;<span class=\"comment\">#这个正则导致我们不能用16进制绕过</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">die</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;no no no!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">intval</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$num</span>,<span class=\"number\">0</span>)==<span class=\"number\">4476</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"variable\">$flag</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">intval</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$num</span>,<span class=\"number\">0</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125; <span class=\"comment\">#num=010574</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"5-科学计数法绕过（php5可以，php7不可以）\"><a href=\"#5-科学计数法绕过（php5可以，php7不可以）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.科学计数法绕过（php5可以，php7不可以）\"></a>5.科学计数法绕过（php5可以，php7不可以）</h2><figure class=\"highlight php\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">intval</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$_GET</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;lover&#x27;</span>]) &lt; <span class=\"number\">2023</span> &amp;&amp; <span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">intval</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$_GET</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;lover&#x27;</span>] + <span class=\"number\">1</span>) &gt; <span class=\"number\">2024</span>) </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>这里既要小于2023，还要+1大于2024，所以我们可以根据他科学计数法的特性，来绕过<strong>lover&#x3D;2e4</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"6-非法变量名传入（php版本小于8）\"><a href=\"#6-非法变量名传入（php版本小于8）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.非法变量名传入（php版本小于8）\"></a>6.非法变量名传入（php版本小于8）</h2><figure class=\"highlight php\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">isset</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$_POST</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;SYC_GEEK.2023&#x27;</span>])&amp;&amp;(<span class=\"variable\">$_POST</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;SYC_GEEK.2023&#x27;</span>]=<span class=\"string\">&quot;Happy to see you!&quot;</span>)) </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>这里仔细观察发现他变量名非法，但是当PHP版本小于8时，如果参数中出现中括号[，中括号会被转换成下划线_，但是会出现转换错误导致接下来如果该参数名中还有非法字符并不会继续转换成下划线_，也就是说如果中括号[出现在前面，那么中括号[还是会被转换成下划线_，但是因为出错导致接下来的非法字符并不会被转换成下划线_。所以<strong>SYC[GEEK.2023&#x3D;1</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"7-strpos-函数绕过\"><a href=\"#7-strpos-函数绕过\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"7.strpos()函数绕过\"></a>7.strpos()函数绕过</h2><p>strpos() 函数查找字符串在另一字符串中第一次出现的位置（区分大小写）。返回字符串在另一字符串中第一次出现的位置，如果没有找到字符串则返回 FALSE。<strong>注释：</strong> 字符串位置从 0 开始，不是从 1 开始。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight php\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">include</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;flag.php&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">highlight_file</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">__FILE__</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">isset</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$_GET</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;num&#x27;</span>]))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"variable\">$num</span> = <span class=\"variable\">$_GET</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;num&#x27;</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$num</span>===<span class=\"string\">&quot;4476&quot;</span>)&#123;<span class=\"comment\">#这里我们不能等于4476字符串</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">die</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;no no no!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">preg_match</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;/[a-z]/i&quot;</span>, <span class=\"variable\">$num</span>))&#123;<span class=\"comment\">#这里是对字母的匹配，无法用16进制</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">die</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;no no no!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(!<span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">strpos</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$num</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;0&quot;</span>))&#123;<span class=\"comment\">#非0就会执行die，所以我们要让他！1，也就是0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">die</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;no no no!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">intval</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$num</span>,<span class=\"number\">0</span>)===<span class=\"number\">4476</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"variable\">$flag</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>所以我们在4476前面加入空格（%20）绕过<strong>num&#x3D;%20010574</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"8-highlight-file-函数绕过\"><a href=\"#8-highlight-file-函数绕过\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"8.highlight_file()函数绕过\"></a>8.highlight_file()函数绕过</h2><p>highlight_file() 函数对文件进行 PHP 语法高亮显示。语法通过使用 HTML 标签进行高亮。</p>\n<p><strong>提示：</strong>用于高亮的颜色可通过 php.ini 文件进行设置或者通过调用 ini_set() 函数进行设置。</p>\n<p><strong>注释：</strong>当使用该函数时，整个文件都将被显示，包括密码和其他敏感信息！</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight php\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">highlight_file</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">__FILE__</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">isset</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$_GET</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;u&#x27;</span>]))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$_GET</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;u&#x27;</span>]==<span class=\"string\">&#x27;flag.php&#x27;</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">die</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;no no no&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"title function_ invoke__\">highlight_file</span>(<span class=\"variable\">$_GET</span>[<span class=\"string\">&#x27;u&#x27;</span>]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>我们不能直接让u&#x3D;flag.php，而是要输入他的完整路径<strong>u&#x3D;&#x2F;var&#x2F;www&#x2F;html&#x2F;flag.php</strong></p>\n<p>一般来说，网站根目录都是**&#x2F;var&#x2F;www&#x2F;html&#x2F;**</p>\n<h2 id=\"9-md5\"><a href=\"#9-md5\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"9.md5\"></a>9.md5</h2><h3 id=\"1-0e绕过\"><a href=\"#1-0e绕过\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.0e绕过\"></a>1.0e绕过</h3><p><strong>0e绕过</strong>：使md5加密后是0exxxxx的形式，在&#x3D;&#x3D;弱比较时，会被当做科学技术法，众所周知，0的任何次方都是0，自然判断为true</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-数组绕过\"><a href=\"#2-数组绕过\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.数组绕过\"></a>2.数组绕过</h3><p><strong>数组绕过</strong>：a[]&#x3D;a&amp;b[]&#x3D;b，&#x3D;&#x3D;传入参数为数组则MD5返回NULL&#x3D;&#x3D;，null&#x3D;null，判断为true，成功绕过</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-md5强比较\"><a href=\"#3-md5强比较\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.md5强比较\"></a>3.md5强比较</h3><p>0e绕过不能用了，因为强比较时，0exxx不再被当做科学计数法，而是被当做字符串。<br><strong>数组绕过仍然可以。</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"10-unserialize（）的-wakerup-绕过\"><a href=\"#10-unserialize（）的-wakerup-绕过\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"10.unserialize（）的__wakerup()绕过\"></a>10.unserialize（）的__wakerup()绕过</h2><h3 id=\"变量引用\"><a href=\"#变量引用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"变量引用\"></a>变量引用</h3><p>两个变量同时指向同一个内存地址</p>\n<p>可利用点为<code>$this-&gt;b=$this-&gt;c;</code>，所以我们可以引用赋值绕过__wakeup()</p>\n<h3 id=\"属性个数不匹配\"><a href=\"#属性个数不匹配\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"属性个数不匹配\"></a>属性个数不匹配</h3><p>影响范围：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>PHP5 &lt; 5.6.25</li>\n<li>PHP7 &lt; 7.0.10</li>\n</ul>\n<p>正常来说在反序列化过程中，会先调用wakeup()方法再进行unserilize()，但如果序列化字符串中表示对象属性个数的值大于真实的属性个数时，wakeup()的执行会被跳过。</p>\n<h3 id=\"C绕过\"><a href=\"#C绕过\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"C绕过\"></a>C绕过</h3><p>O标识符代表对象类型，而C标识符代表类名类型。如果将O替换为C，则在反序列化时会将其解释为一个新的类名字符串，从而创建一个新的类而不是对象。因为这个新的类没有被序列化过，所以它没有任何属性或方法。这样一来，在反序列化时，__wakeup魔术方法就不会被自动调用。</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"php特性1.preg_matchpreg_match 是 PHP 中用于执行正则表达式匹配的函数。它的主要特性包括： 正则表达式匹配：preg_match 允...","permalink":"/post/php特性","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"6.1k","symbolsTime":"6 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"web","slug":"web","count":2,"path":"api/categories/web.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"ctf-web","slug":"ctf-web","count":2,"path":"api/tags/ctf-web.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#php%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7\"><span class=\"toc-text\">php特性</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-preg-match\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.preg_match</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E5%8F%AA%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.只检测数字</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E5%8F%AA%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%E5%AD%97%E6%AF%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.只检测字母</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E8%BD%AC%E5%8C%96%E6%88%90%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E8%A6%81%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.不能是字符串，但是转化成数字要等于</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E-i%E5%92%8C-im%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.对于&#x2F;i和&#x2F;im绕过</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#4-intval-variable-base-%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">4.intval(variable, base)绕过</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%85%AB%E8%BF%9B%E5%88%B6%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">八进制绕过</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#5-%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E8%AE%A1%E6%95%B0%E6%B3%95%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87%EF%BC%88php5%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%EF%BC%8Cphp7%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">5.科学计数法绕过（php5可以，php7不可以）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#6-%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E5%90%8D%E4%BC%A0%E5%85%A5%EF%BC%88php%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8E8%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">6.非法变量名传入（php版本小于8）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#7-strpos-%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">7.strpos()函数绕过</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#8-highlight-file-%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">8.highlight_file()函数绕过</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#9-md5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">9.md5</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-0e%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.0e绕过</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.数组绕过</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-md5%E5%BC%BA%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.md5强比较</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#10-unserialize%EF%BC%88%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84-wakerup-%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">10.unserialize（）的__wakerup()绕过</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">变量引用</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%E4%B8%AA%E6%95%B0%E4%B8%8D%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\">属性个数不匹配</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#C%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">C绕过</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"yona-lia","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/jmy.png","link":"/","description":"一个正在努力学习的小菜鸡","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"零碎芝士","uid":"b05e548a184fbeb6a9a7d59d98c56d2d","slug":"零碎芝士","date":"2024-01-21T16:10:24.000Z","updated":"2024-01-21T16:27:28.154Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/零碎芝士.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"1.Ctrl + U在大多数现代网页浏览器中，按下 Ctrl + U 键组合将打开当前网页的源代码视图。这个快捷键通常用于查看网页的 HTML、CSS 和 Ja...","permalink":"/post/零碎芝士","photos":[],"